I"F<p>Robo Chase is a <strong>local two-player retro platformer</strong>, with one player playing as a cop chasing to catch the other player playing as a robot, while avoiding a wall of laser coming at them, among other obstacles and traps. It’s played on a split screen and the game ends when either player dies, the cop catches the robot or the robot makes it to the end of the level. <!--more-->The game was made as an entry to the <a href="https://itch.io/jam/retro-platformer-jam">Retro Platformer Jam</a>, and we ended up getting 1st place in the “Technical” category.</p>
